* Create Column\nMask Policies
** Purpose
***_ Control what values users see
***_ Mask sensitive column data
** Masking UDF
***_ Returns masked/redacted value
***_ Same data type as input column
** CREATE POLICY syntax
***_ ON SCHEMA / CATALOG
***_ COLUMN MASK <function>
***_ TO principal EXCEPT exempt_group
***_ MATCH COLUMNS hasTagValue(...)
** Example
***_ SSN → '***-**-****'
***_ Only compliance_team sees real values
** Applies to
***_ Columns tagged with specified tag
***_ Scope: schema or catalog level
@endmindmap
